2	// SessionActor — Durable Object that holds SSE connections and
3	// broadcasts HTML fragments to all connected clients.
4	//
5	// Pure message bus: no domain logic, no D1 mutations. The SDK is
6	// only used here — route handlers never import it.
7	// ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
